				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>This is great post-apocalyptic comovedy &#8211; vintage! The mood is great, I was reminded of oryx and crake (which was my initial interpretation of the theme). The first paragraph is great and traumatic, but the context is not entirely clear &#8211; same with the reference to the dome from your previous story. I am interested in how those things fit together and would like to know more! </p>
<p>I loved the ending &#8211; the breed is obscure enough to give a double take <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

